# append(contentsOf:)

**Instance Method**

Appends the elements of the given column to the end of this column.

## Declaration

```swift
mutating func append(contentsOf newColumn: MLUntypedColumn)
```

## Parameters

- **newColumn**: Another column to append to the column.
